0\u0431\u043b\u0438\u0446\u0430 2\u0421. \u041c.: \u0424\u0435\u0434\u0435\u0440\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u0430\u044f \u0441\u043b\u0443\u0436\u0431\u0430 \u0433\u043e\u0441\u0443\u0434\u0430\u0440\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0435\u043d\u043d\u043e\u0439 \u0441\u0442\u0430\u0442\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0438\u043a\u0438, 2004.</ref> \n\n== Geography ==\nThe distance to [[Ustye, Ust-Kubinsky District, Vologda Oblast|Ustye]] is 3.5&nbsp;km. Ustye is the nearest rural locality.\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Rural localities in Ust-Kubinsky District}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Rural localities in Vologda Oblast]]\n[[Category:Rural localities in Ust-Kubinsky District]]\n\n{{VologdaOblast-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n|official_name          = Zaluzhye\n|other_name             = \n|native_name            = \u0417\u0430\u043b\u0443\u0436\u044c\u0435\n|nickname               = \n|settlement_type        = Village\n|image_skyline          = \n|image_caption          = \n|pushpin_map            = Russia Vologda Oblast#Russia\n|pushpin_label_position = \n|pushpin_mapsize        =\n|pushpin_map_caption    = \n|subdivision_type       = Country\n|subdivision_name       = [[Russia]]\n|subdivision_type1      = [[List of regions of Russia|Region]] \n|subdivision_name1      = [[Vologda Oblast]]\n|subdivision_type2      = [[Counties of Russia|County]] \n|subdivision_name2      = \n|subdivision_type3      = [[Districts of Russia|District]] \n|subdivision_name3      = [[Ust-Kubinsky District]]\n|subdivision_type4      = [[List of municipalities of Russia|Municipality]]\n|subdivision_name4      = \n|timezone1              = \n|utc_offset1            = +3:00\n|timezone1_DST          = \n|utc_offset1_DST        = \n|postal_code_type       = \n|postal_code            = \n|elevation_m            = \n|elevation_footnotes    = \n|coordinates            = {{coord|59|38|N|39|46|E|display=inline}}<ref>[https://mapdata.ru/vologodskaya-oblast/ust-kubinskiy-rayon/ \u041a\u0430\